window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From </b><b><i>USA Today</i></b><b> bestselling author Brynne Asher comes a thrilling romance that will leave you so twisted, you won't know which way is up.</b></p> <p>I'm driven by an obsession for a man who's turning out to be dark, dangerous, and downright depraved.</p> <p>It all started with an auction. I couldn't help myself. There was no way I was going to allow another woman to win a date with the broody firefighter who fascinated me from the beginning. I paid a ridiculous amount of money that I couldn't afford for one night with him, but when my instincts took over, there was no going back.</p> <p>Brand Vitale might look like a hero to the rest of the world, but looks can be deceiving. He's no typical hero. But then again, I'm no fairy tale princess. Even if I did lose a shoe.</p> <p>Brand barged into my life, took me by the hand, and led me straight into a world of secrets, rival mafia families, and murder. I didn't just follow him. I jumped.</p> <p>And it turns out, my obsession is nothing compared to his burning desire to make me his. Because with a passion this deep, you have no option but to love... straight to death.</p>"; 
